             <li class="cbt-feature-item"><strong>Therapist-Guided Support:</strong> Each page includes therapist-facing notes, prompts, and examples for easy explanation.</li>
             <li class="cbt-feature-item"><strong>Reusable:</strong> Whiteboard-style pages let you write, erase, and reuse during multiple sessions.</li>
             <li class="cbt-feature-item"><strong>Designed for Clinical Use:</strong> Professional-grade materials built for frequent in-office use by clinicians, social workers, and psychologists.</li>
